  "text": "In the 1990s and 2000s, SOE restructuring was implemented in tandem with promotion of private enterprises. In 1995, radical reforms of SOEs started amid their deteriorating performance (particularly profitability and output growth) since the late 1980s [CITATION_1] . Reform directions were gradually developed over the years. For example, in November 1993, the CCP's",
